data.description: Welcome to Riverwood Estates, your ideal country retreat! This charming home boasts 3 bedrooms (2 dual Primary suites) and 2  bathrooms, offering an open concept living space and inviting atmosphere that is perfect for entertaining. The home sits on over 2.35 acres of open pasture; features several upgrades:new water softener, granite countertops, well house, Alan Factory detached 2 car garage equipped with 3 roll up doors, carport and 2 sheds which provide ample space for your vehicles and extra storage. This property presents endless possibilities for outdoor activities and potential future expansions.  But that's not all, you can indulge in your backyard oasis featuring a flagstone patio and sparkling pool, which is ideal for relaxation on hot summer days. Its secluded location ensures peace and tranquility, away from the hustle and bustle of city life, allowing you to truly appreciate the beauty of nature. Schedule a visit today and embark on a new chapter of peaceful living!
